The review criteria, stated below, which were established in FY 1990 (55 FR 12424, dated 4/3/90) after public comment,
will remain unchanged in FY 1995. 

 The extent to which the proposed project meets the legislative purpose; 

 The background and rationale for the proposed project; 

 The extent to which the project contains clearly stated realistic and achievable objectives; 



