August 35, 1994. 



Pursuant to Section 19(b)(1) of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934 (``Act''), 15 U.S.C. 78s(b)(1), and Rule 19b-4
thereunder, notice is hereby given that on August 18, 1994, the Municipal Securities Rulemaking Board (``Board''
