and resident groups identified above. The package shall contain a description of Youth Leadership and the training
to be offered, which will be targeted to housing authority teams comprised of housing authority staff, adult and 

youth residents, and, as appropriate, participants from other local organizations. This application kit will be
used by the grantee and the Department to select the participants for the workshop. The grantee will be responsible
